    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:0",
      "text": "passes tab 的主要用途是为 render 创建 additional outputs。这些输出也称为",
      "ascii_letters": 32,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:1",
      "text": "Arbitrary Output Variables",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:3",
      "text": "也可以创建额外的 \"passes\"，它们更类似 Maya 的 render layers（也受支持）。每个 pass 都可以拥有自己的 camera 和 render settings，用作 global render settings 的 overrides。",
      "ascii_letters": 75,
      "cjk_chars": 32
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:4",
      "text": "此 UI 可用于创建 Display Channels（AOV selections 和 LPE sources）以及作为目标文件（TIFF、OpenEXR 等）的 Display Drivers。默认情况下，双击会把左侧 menu 中的新 Display Channel 和 Driver 添加到右侧 menu。左侧 menu 包含 rendering 常用的 preset AOVs 和 LPE。它们分为以下 categories：",
      "ascii_letters": 129,
      "cjk_chars": 51
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:6",
      "text": "输入你自己的 custom AOV 或 LPE",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:7",
      "text": "Standard:",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:9",
      "text": "built-in AOVs",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:11",
      "text": "Diagnostic:",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:12",
      "text": "这里包含一部分 AOVs，用于可视化 pixel samples 和 CPU Time 等。",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:13",
      "text": "Lighting:",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:16",
      "text": "；direct diffuse、indirect specular 等 outputs 都在这里。",
      "ascii_letters": 36,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:17",
      "text": "Denoiser:",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:20",
      "text": "utility 使用；选择 beauty Display Driver 并启用 Denoise 后，Batch Render 之后会对 Beauty denoise。",
      "ascii_letters": 57,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:24",
      "text": "这些 Matte LPE 需配合",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:25",
      "text": "PxrMatteID",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:26",
      "text": "Integrator:",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:28",
      "text": "Integrator",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:30",
      "text": "简短说明：双击左侧要 render 的 Channels。这样会自动创建一个同名的新 display driver 进行 rendering。",
      "ascii_letters": 36,
      "cjk_chars": 25
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:31",
      "text": "如果你想要较短的列表，或希望这些 channels 输出到单个 file，请在使用 Channels box 左下角的 arrow-to-list button 添加 Channels 时，确保右侧已选中一个 Display Driver。",
      "ascii_letters": 61,
      "cjk_chars": 40
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:33",
      "text": "第一次打开 AOV tab 时，你会看到 default render pass 的 outputs。",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:34",
      "text": "Displays",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:35",
      "text": "Displays tab 显示所选 pass 的 outputs。它们位于右侧列表中。Final pass 的默认 output 如预期是 rgba，即典型图像的 color (Ci) 和 alpha (a) channels。你可以从左侧 preset 列表选择其他 outputs，并点击两个列表之间的 arrow button 添加。",
      "ascii_letters": 86,
      "cjk_chars": 52
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:36",
      "text": "Custom outputs",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:38",
      "text": "每个 output 都有自己的 settings；在 outputs 列表中选中 item 后，这些 settings 会显示在列表下方。双击已有 preset 会将其添加到 render 列表中，首先列出 Display Driver (_directDiffuse)，其下方是 Display Channel（source，directDiffuse）。下面先说明 Display Drivers 的选项。",
      "ascii_letters": 118,
      "cjk_chars": 53
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:39",
      "text": "Display Settings",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:41",
      "text": "允许此 output 进行 render",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:42",
      "text": "Display Type",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:43",
      "text": "选择 Display Driver 的 output file format，包括 Deep Data (DeepEXR)",
      "ascii_letters": 44,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:45",
      "text": "OpenEXR 是 render 最常用、通用且功能强的 file format。它是默认且推荐的 file type。",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:46",
      "text": "Denoise 功能需要 OpenEXR 或 TIFF types",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:49",
      "text": "按 RGBA 顺序排列 Channels",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:51",
      "text": "Tiled：Image 会保存为 tile-formatted data blocks",
      "ascii_letters": 33,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:52",
      "text": "Planar：保存为 scanline format",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:54",
      "text": "Half Precision (16-half)",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:55",
      "text": "Float Precision (32-bit float)",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:56",
      "text": "通常 Half 对 color AOVs 和 passes 已经足够。对于 Z depth 或 P 等 Data AOVs 和 passes，建议使用 Float。OpenEXR 不支持更低 bit depths。",
      "ascii_letters": 61,
      "cjk_chars": 22
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:57",
      "text": "Compression",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:58",
      "text": "ZIPS 是默认值，建议用于 compositing workflow，因为它按单条 scanline 存储",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:59",
      "text": "ZIP 也有用，但在 compositing packages 中以 16 条 scanlines 为 bundle 时会稍慢",
      "ascii_letters": 37,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:61",
      "text": "Wiki page",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:63",
      "text": "Compression Level",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:67",
      "text": "Image Tool",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:68",
      "text": "作为 display device；没有其他选项。",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:70",
      "text": "DeepEXR 是用于存储 deep data 的常见 format，即 per-sample data，可用于在 depth 上 composite objects，例如 Volumes 中嵌套的 objects",
      "ascii_letters": 69,
      "cjk_chars": 20
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:72",
      "text": "Tiled：Image 会保存为 tile-formatted data blocks",
      "ascii_letters": 33,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:73",
      "text": "Planar：保存为 scanline format",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:75",
      "text": "Half Precision (16-half)",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:76",
      "text": "Float Precision (32-bit float)",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:77",
      "text": "通常 Half 对 color AOVs 和 passes 已经足够。对于 Z depth 或 P 等 Data AOVs 和 passes，建议使用 Float。",
      "ascii_letters": 45,
      "cjk_chars": 17
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:78",
      "text": "Compression",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:79",
      "text": "我们在内部自动处理 samples merging，以在 size 和 correctness 之间取得最佳 balance；因此下面这些选项可用于控制 output frames 的最终 size。",
      "ascii_letters": 52,
      "cjk_chars": 34
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:80",
      "text": "ZIPS 是默认值，建议用于 compositing workflow，因为它按单条 scanline 存储",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:81",
      "text": "ZIP 也有用，但在 compositing packages 中以 16 条 scanlines 为 bundle 时会稍慢",
      "ascii_letters": 37,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:83",
      "text": "Wiki page",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:86",
      "text": "PNG 是常见 web format，包含用于 transparency 的 Alpha channel",
      "ascii_letters": 36,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:87",
      "text": "Quantize",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:88",
      "text": "此选项会尝试压缩 color scheme 以缩小 file size",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:90",
      "text": "Targa 是一种流行的 8-bit（per channel）file format",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:91",
      "text": "Quantize",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:92",
      "text": "此选项会尝试压缩 color scheme 以缩小 file size",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:94",
      "text": "这会直接从 renderer render 到 RenderMan .tex format。",
      "ascii_letters": 32,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:95",
      "text": "用于此项的 image resolution 预计应具有 power-of-two dimensions，并且必须由用户设置。例如 512 x 512（其中 512 是 power of two 且为 square）",
      "ascii_letters": 52,
      "cjk_chars": 26
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:96",
      "text": "Texture Format",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:98",
      "text": "OpenEXR：保存为 OpenEXR format",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:99",
      "text": "Tiff：保存为 TIFF format（注意此 format 不能保存大于 4GB 的 files）",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:100",
      "text": "Bit Depth",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:101",
      "text": "设置 output file 的 bit depth；不适用于 OpenEXR",
      "ascii_letters": 25,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:103",
      "text": "Short：小文件，比 Byte 包含更多 data",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:104",
      "text": "Float：文件较大，可保持 full precision",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:105",
      "text": "EXR Bit Depth",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:106",
      "text": "Half Precision (16-half)",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:107",
      "text": "Float Precision (32-bit float)",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:108",
      "text": "S and T Wrap Modes",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:109",
      "text": "black：适用于 UDIM 等 tile-based workflows。",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:110",
      "text": "clamp：适用于 non-periodic texturing access。",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:111",
      "text": "periodic：适用于周期性的 periodic（repeating）texture access。",
      "ascii_letters": 38,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:112",
      "text": "Compression",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:113",
      "text": "None：不执行 compression",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:114",
      "text": "Lossless：执行 compression，但不损失 precision",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:115",
      "text": "Lossy：通过移除 details 进行 compression 并进一步减小 size",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:116",
      "text": "EXR Compression",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:117",
      "text": "我们在内部自动处理 samples merging，以在 size 和 correctness 之间取得最佳 balance；因此下面这些选项可用于控制 output frames 的最终 size。",
      "ascii_letters": 52,
      "cjk_chars": 34
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:118",
      "text": "ZIPS 是默认值，建议用于 compositing workflow，因为它按单条 scanline 存储",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:119",
      "text": "ZIP 也有用，但在 compositing packages 中以 16 条 scanlines 为 bundle 时会稍慢",
      "ascii_letters": 37,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:121",
      "text": "Wiki page",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:123",
      "text": "EXR Compression Level",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:126",
      "text": "Tiff 是常见 format，也可以存储 floating point precision images 以及 pass data",
      "ascii_letters": 46,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:128",
      "text": "uint8：8-bit storage。file size 小，通常不适合 post compositing work。",
      "ascii_letters": 41,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:129",
      "text": "uint16：16-bit integer storage。file size 小，比 8-bit counterpart 有更好的 reproduction。",
      "ascii_letters": 55,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:130",
      "text": "float32：完整 32-bit float images。file size 更大，但最适合 post compositing。",
      "ascii_letters": 42,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:131",
      "text": "Quantize",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:132",
      "text": "此选项会尝试压缩 color scheme 以缩小 file size",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:133",
      "text": "Compression",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:134",
      "text": "None：不执行 compression，file 为 full size 且 lossless",
      "ascii_letters": 35,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:135",
      "text": "LZW：TIFF files 中非常常见的 lossless compression。",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:136",
      "text": "Packbits (RLE)：快速 lossless compression，compression 率低于 LZW",
      "ascii_letters": 44,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:137",
      "text": "Deflate：常见 lossless compression scheme",
      "ascii_letters": 32,
      "cjk_chars": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:138",
      "text": "Pixarlog：通常适合压缩 HDR images，同时不丢失 highlight data",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:139",
      "text": "Resolution Unit",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:140",
      "text": "在 inches、centimeters 或 none 之间选择。这类似于告诉 Maya 你的 per-unit resolution。",
      "ascii_letters": 42,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:141",
      "text": "Resolution",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:142",
      "text": "ImageWidth 和 ImageHeight 方向中每个 Resolution Unit（上方）的 pixels 数。",
      "ascii_letters": 41,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:144",
      "text": "为所选 Display 启用 denoising",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:146",
      "text": "Single Frame 用于 still render 的单帧渲染",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:147",
      "text": "Cross-frame 用于 animation 或一系列 frames",
      "ascii_letters": 25,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:150",
      "text": "Filtering documentation",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:151",
      "text": "Break Point：color 保持不变的阈值下限，必须为 non-negative (a)",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:152",
      "text": "Max Value：包含的 max value；为 0 时所有 remapping 关闭。它不能小于 Break Point value。(b)",
      "ascii_letters": 41,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:153",
      "text": "Smoothness：对 breakpoint 处 second derivative 的 tweak（除非 a==b，否则 function 是 C(1)，因此你无法指定 first derivative。如果此 parameter 为 1，function 为 C(2)。较小 values 会让它更 flat，较大 values 会让它 less flat。如果大于 ~2.5，curve 会有 inflection point，即在 breakpoint 右侧向上弯曲。设置 c <= 0 是 illegal 的，且不建议将它设为除 1 以外的任何值。default value 为 0。",
      "ascii_letters": 159,
      "cjk_chars": 65
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:154",
      "text": "Display Channels",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:155",
      "text": "Display Channels 是上方 display drivers 使用的 sources。通常添加 new AOVs 时，双击会添加一个 new AOV 以及一个 display driver。这意味着你的 AOVs 会被拆分到不同 outputs。",
      "ascii_letters": 73,
      "cjk_chars": 35
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:157",
      "text": "添加 display channel 后，可以查看它的 settings",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:158",
      "text": "Display Channel Settings",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:160",
      "text": "设置此 channel 是否 renderable。",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:161",
      "text": "Channel Type",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:162",
      "text": "data 使用的 types 通常存储为支持 floating point 的 formats，例如 OpenEXR 或 Float Tiff",
      "ascii_letters": 45,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:168",
      "text": "Channel Source",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:169",
      "text": "这是 AOV 的 source，通常是在此处指定用于 rendering 的 LPE。",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:170",
      "text": "LPE Light Group",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:171",
      "text": "你可以在这里手动指定 light group，使其匹配已分配给 lights 的 light groups；也可以使用 dropdown menu 从 lights 中已指定的现有 light groups 中选择。这允许 per-light (group) LPE output。",
      "ascii_letters": 78,
      "cjk_chars": 38
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:172",
      "text": "如果在 UI 打开时向 lights 添加了 new light groups，可能需要关闭 render settings 和/或添加 new LPE；这会强制它从场景重新填充 groups 到 menu choices。",
      "ascii_letters": 59,
      "cjk_chars": 33
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:174",
      "text": "你可以使用此 section 来 override",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:175",
      "text": "specified filter",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:176",
      "text": "。对于大多数 color data，继承的 filter 最好，这样可以匹配其他 AOVs；但对于 data，你可能希望使用列出的 min、max、zmin、zmax 等 filters 之一，以避免跨 object edges 进行 filtering。",
      "ascii_letters": 64,
      "cjk_chars": 40
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:177",
      "text": "Filter Width",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:179",
      "text": "Statistics",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:180",
      "text": "这些选项并非专门面向 artists；它们对 pipeline considerations 或 renderer 外部的 denoise applications 可能有用，并不是必需使用。它们作为 pipeline 的实用工具暴露出来，因此你不必直接修改 RIB files。",
      "ascii_letters": 72,
      "cjk_chars": 50
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:181",
      "text": "Variance:",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:182",
      "text": "估计 associated source channel 中 contributing to pixel 的 values 的 statistical variance。",
      "ascii_letters": 67,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:184",
      "text": "类似 variance，但会随着 samples 数增加而趋近于 zero。虽然它本身也有些 noisy，但可以为 mean-squared-error 相对于 hypothetical ground-truth image 的大小提供估计。",
      "ascii_letters": 68,
      "cjk_chars": 35
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:186",
      "text": "将 even numbered samples render 到此 AOV",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:188",
      "text": "将 odd numbered samples render 到此 AOV",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:191",
      "text": "Filtering documentation",
      "ascii_letters": 22,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:192",
      "text": "Break Point：color 保持不变的阈值下限，必须为 non-negative (a)",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:193",
      "text": "Max Value：包含的 max value；为 0 时所有 remapping 关闭。它不能小于 Break Point value。(b)",
      "ascii_letters": 41,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "2640afd3dc:194",
      "text": "Smoothness：对 breakpoint 处 second derivative 的 tweak（除非 a==b，否则 function 是 C(1)，因此你无法指定 first derivative。如果此 parameter 为 1，function 为 C(2)。较小 values 会让它更 flat，较大 values 会让它 less flat。如果大于 ~2.5，curve 会有 inflection point，即在 breakpoint 右侧向上弯曲。设置 c <= 0 是 illegal 的，且不建议将它设为除 1 以外的任何值。default value 为 0。",
      "ascii_letters": 159,
      "cjk_chars": 65
    }
